  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Harmonization and Social Cohesion Programme Across Turkey</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to support the harmonization of migrants in line with Turkey&apos;s new migration management framework and EU approaches.  Implementation of an effective approach on harmonization is a critical goal for DGMM particularly with increasing social tensions. To be successful, a national programme with locally tailored initiatives requires the government and partners such as IOM to target the following needs: information services to facilitate migrants&apos; access to services and rights; establishment and/or strengthening of locally managed social cohesion programmes; capacity development of DGMM/PDMM and ministry staff at federal and provincial levels.</narrative>
  </description>
